{"tid":1147004,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"豹紋女士羅美蘭 最新潮流服飾","createTime":"2019-05-09T14:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T16:27:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9bd9f1db32133c4a2ad74ce71cd3638eadb2db","tid":1147004,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"羅美蘭出演過非常受大家喜愛的電視劇請回答1988，也是因為這個劇，羅美蘭才有了豹子這個稱號，甚至國內的小夥伴親切的稱她是豹子女士。<br />\n因為在請回答1988中，羅美蘭每一次的造型，都會有豹紋的元素。但是羅美蘭的豹紋裝，受到了很多人的喜愛。甚至在電視劇走紅之後，羅美蘭還穿着豹子服裝，拍攝了很多雜誌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/5b419b404ac2858031c160d7bfdf3d21/5D5AB769/t51.2885-15/e35/58772405_407986483115811_7615306250601438084_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F5b419b404ac2858031c160d7bfdf3d21%2F5D5AB769%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F58772405_407986483115811_7615306250601438084_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net&h=030bd056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/7e86f03ed6136cc18a2e60f877b6b5df/5D65232D/t51.2885-15/e35/58423691_2746945255377799_3386629446910317827_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F7e86f03ed6136cc18a2e60f877b6b5df%2F5D65232D%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F58423691_2746945255377799_3386629446910317827_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net&h=e1317fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/1e3dd628d53ca6aed113f0032b0d0243/5D59EC15/t51.2885-15/e35/58858150_2306338619409839_8181536518179900088_n.jpg?_nc_ht=instagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F1e3dd628d53ca6aed113f0032b0d0243%2F5D59EC15%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F58858150_2306338619409839_8181536518179900088_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dinstagram.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn